ex_colors}\")\n\n# ðŸš€ RUN (Upload an image called 'scene.jpg' to test)\n# get_dominant_colors('scene.jpg') \nprint(\"Copy this code, upload a movie frame, and run!\")","metadata":{"_uuid":"8f2839f25d086af736a60e9eeb907d3b93b6e0e5","_cell_guid":"b1076dfc-b9ad-4769-8c92-a6c4dae69d19","trusted":true,"execution":{"iopub.status.busy":"2026-01-19T00:20:52.375811Z","iopub.execute_input":"2026-01-19T00:20:52.376118Z","iopub.status.idle":"2026-01-19T00:20:56.866355Z","shell.execute_reply.started":"2026-01-19T00:20:52.376082Z","shell.execute_reply":"2026-01-19T00:20:56.865186Z"}},"outputs":[{"name":"stdout","text":"Copy this code, upload a movie frame, and run!\n","output_type":"stream"}],"execution_count":1},{"cell_type":"code","source":"# En fin","metadata":{"trusted":true},"outputs":[],"execution_count":null}]}